title: Uncle Josh's Punkin Centre Stories
creator: Cal Stewart
description: LibriVox recording of Uncle Josh's Punkin Centre Stories, by Cal Stewart. Read by Philip Martin. A collection of comedic short stories from the perspective of an old country man. (Summary by Philip Martin) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
